u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15670,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/14\/fasting-or-not-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35681,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Fasting or not on the day of Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I have performed the Hajj pilgrimage with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he did not fast during Arafat. I performed it with Abu Bakr and he did not fast, with Umar and he did not fast, and with Uthman and he did not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/ten-sahabah-promised-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35681,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Ten companions promised Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdur Rahman ibn 'Awf reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAbu Bakr is in Paradise. Umar is in Paradise. Uthman is in Paradise. Ali is in Paradise. Talhah is in Paradise. Al-Zubayr is in Paradise. Abdur Rahman ibn 'Awf is in Paradise. Sa\u2019d is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/fait